Class CWTClaimsSetBuilder

java.lang.Object
com.authlete.cwt.CWTClaimsSetBuilder
public class CWTClaimsSetBuilder extends Object
A utility to build an instance of the CWTClaimsSet class.
Since:
1.4
See Also:
